<h3 id="toc0"><span><span style="color: #c21664">Losing My Colors</span></span></h3>
<h4 id="toc1"><span><span style="color: #c21664">Tale based on <a href="/scp-4319">SCP-4319</a></span></span></h4>
<p><span style="color: #c21664"><strong>Author:</strong></span> <span class="error-inline"><em>AlanDaris</em> does not match any existing user name</span></p>
